{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775841089144,"sessionID":"ses_2879fdfa1ffeKs2oss1t7eSJfW","part":{"id":"prt_d78608e58001CAHaUqD6T4qRMG","messageID":"msg_d7860796b001SJSCCiyZnLBlte","sessionID":"ses_2879fdfa1ffeKs2oss1t7eSJfW","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-b83983b9e86e46b3b36a326b23027ba5","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-003/spec.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-003/spec.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-003 — CRD 共享类型与常量\n2: \n3: ## Metadata\n4: \n5: | Item | Value |\n6: |------|-------|\n7: | AR | AR-003 — CRD 共享类型与常量 |\n8: | Module | `pkg/apis` |\n9: | Language | Go |\n10: | Size | S |\n11: | Stage | ST-0 |\n12: \n13: ## Scope\n14: \n15: 定义 CRD 共享类型和常量，包括:\n16: - `TargetPort` 类型（端口配置）\n17: - `ProtocolType` 枚举（HTTP/HTTPS）\n18: - `AuthModeType` 枚举（picod/none）\n19: - Label/Annotation 常量\n20: - Condition Type 常量\n21: - 默认值常量\n22: \n23: ## Out of Scope\n24: \n25: - Controller 实现\n26: - Webhook 验证逻辑\n27: - CRD YAML 生成\n28: - client-go 代码生成\n29: \n30: ## Dependencies\n31: \n32: 无外部依赖，为 AR-001、AR-002 提供共享类型。\n33: \n34: ## Deliverables\n35: \n36: | File | Description |\n37: |------|-------------|\n38: | `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/shared_types.go` | 共享类型和常量定义 |\n39: \n40: ## Acceptance Criteria\n41: \n42: - [ ] 共享类型定义符合 Kubernetes API conventions\n43: - [ ] 常量命名遵循统一命名规范\n44: - [ ] 包含完整的 godoc 注释\n45: - [ ] 通过 `go vet` 和 `golangci-lint`\n46: - [ ] Enum 验证标记正确\n47: \n48: ## References\n49: \n50: - Kubernetes API Conventions: https://git.k8s.io/community/contributors/devel/sig-architecture/api-conventions.md\n51: - AR-001 Design: `changes/AR-001/design.md`\n52: - AR-002 Design: `changes/AR-002/design.md`\n\n(End of file - total 52 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-003 — CRD 共享类型与常量\n\n## Metadata\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-003 — CRD 共享类型与常量 |\n| Module | `pkg/apis` |\n| Language | Go |\n| Size | S |\n| Stage | ST-0 |\n\n## Scope\n\n定义 CRD 共享类型和常量，包括:\n- `TargetPort` 类型（端口配置）\n- `ProtocolType` 枚举（HTTP/HTTPS）\n- `AuthModeType` 枚举（picod/none）\n- Label/Annotation 常量\n- Condition Type 常量","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-003/spec.md","time":{"start":1775841089120,"end":1775841089143}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775841089147,"sessionID":"ses_2879fdfa1ffeKs2oss1t7eSJfW","part":{"id":"prt_d7860926f001vpAa8C2QR8APir","messageID":"msg_d7860796b001SJSCCiyZnLBlte","sessionID":"ses_2879fdfa1ffeKs2oss1t7eSJfW","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-2c0f2734f9ca48da82a031e835cee814","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-003/design.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-003/design.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-003 — CRD 共享类型与常量 Design\n2: \n3: ## Overview\n4: \n5: | Item | Value |\n6: |------|-------|\n7: | AR | AR-003 — CRD 共享类型与常量 |\n8: | Module | `pkg/apis` |\n9: | Language | Go |\n10: | Size | S |\n11: | Stage | ST-1 |\n12: \n13: 定义 CRD 共享类型和常量，供 AgentRuntime 和 CodeInterpreter CRD 使用。API group: `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`。\n14: \n15: ## Design\n16: \n17: ### Architecture\n18: \n19: 共享类型和常量定义遵循 Kubernetes API conventions：\n20: - 类型定义使用 `kubebuilder` markers 生成 OpenAPI schema\n21: - 常量使用统一命名规范（LabelKey*, AnnotationKey*, ConditionType*）\n22: - 默认值常量供 controller 使用\n23: - 所有定义位于 `shared_types.go`，便于集中管理\n24: \n25: ### Dependencies\n26: \n27: | Package | Purpose |\n28: |---------|---------|\n29: | (无外部依赖) | 共享类型为基础定义 |\n30: \n31: ### Controller-gen Markers\n32: \n33: | Marker | Applied to | Purpose |\n34: |--------|------------|---------|\n35: | `+kubebuilder:validation:Enum` | ProtocolType, AuthModeType | 枚举验证 |\n36: | `+kubebuilder:default` | TargetPort.Protocol | 默认值 |\n37: \n38: ## Data Structures\n39: \n40: ### Shared Types\n41: \n42: #### ProtocolType\n43: \n44: ```go\n45: // ProtocolType defines the protocol for a target port.\n46: // +kubebuilder:validation:Enum=HTTP;HTTPS\n47: type ProtocolType string\n48: \n49: const (\n50:     // ProtocolTypeHTTP indicates HTTP protocol.\n51:     ProtocolTypeHTTP  ProtocolType = \"HTTP\"\n52:     // ProtocolTypeHTTPS indicates HTTPS protocol.\n53:     ProtocolTypeHTTPS ProtocolType = \"HTTPS\"\n54: )\n55: ```\n56: \n57: #### AuthModeType\n58: \n59: ```go\n60: // AuthModeType defines the authentication mode for a CodeInterpreter.\n61: // +kubebuilder:validation:Enum=picod;none\n62: type AuthModeType string\n63: \n64: const (\n65:     // AuthModePicoD indicates pico authentication mode.\n66:     AuthModePicoD AuthModeType = \"picod\"\n67:     // AuthModeNone indicates no authentication.\n68:     AuthModeNone  AuthModeType = \"none\"\n69: )\n70: ```\n71: \n72: #### TargetPort\n73: \n74: ```go\n75: // TargetPort defines a network port configuration for exposing sandbox services.\n76: type TargetPort struct {\n77:     // PathPrefix is the URL path prefix for routing to this port.\n78:     // +optional\n79:     PathPrefix string `json:\"pathPrefix,omitempty\"`\n80: \n81:     // Name is a human-readable name for this port.\n82:     // +optional\n83:     Name string `json:\"name,omitempty\"`\n84: \n85:     // Port is the container port number to expose.\n86:     Port uint32 `json:\"port\"`\n87: \n88:     // Protocol specifies the protocol for this port (HTTP or HTTPS).\n89:     // +kubebuilder:default=HTTP\n90:     // +kubebuilder:validation:Enum=HTTP;HTTPS\n91:     Protocol ProtocolType `json:\"protocol\"`\n92: }\n93: ```\n94: \n95: ### Constants\n96: \n97: #### Label Constants\n98: \n99: Labels 用于标识沙箱资源的元数据，遵循 `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/<key>` 格式：\n100: \n101: ```go\n102: const (\n103:     // LabelKeyOwnerRuntime indicates the owning AgentRuntime/CodeInterpreter name.\n104:     LabelKeyOwnerRuntime = \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/owner-runtime\"\n105: \n106:     // LabelKeyOwnerKind indicates the owning CRD kind (AgentRuntime/CodeInterpreter).\n107:     LabelKeyOwnerKind = \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/owner-kind\"\n108: \n109:     // LabelKeySessionID indicates the active session identifier.\n110:     LabelKeySessionID = \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/session-id\"\n111: \n112:     // LabelKeySandboxType indicates the sandbox type (agent/code-interpreter).\n113:     LabelKeySandboxType = \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/sandbox-type\"\n114: \n115:     // LabelKeySandboxTypeAgent indicates an agent sandbox.\n116:     LabelKeySandboxTypeAgent = \"agent\"\n117: \n118:     // LabelKeySandboxTypeCodeInterpreter indicates a code interpreter sandbox.\n119:     LabelKeySandboxTypeCodeInterpreter = \"code-interpreter\"\n120: )\n121: ```\n122: \n123: #### Annotation Constants\n124: \n125: Annotations 用于存储运行时配置和状态信息：\n126: \n127: ```go\n128: const (\n129:     // AnnotationKeyAuthMode stores the authentication mode for the sandbox.\n130:     AnnotationKeyAuthMode = \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/auth-mode\"\n131: \n132:     // AnnotationKeySessionStart stores the session start timestamp.\n133:     AnnotationKeySessionStart = \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/session-start\"\n134: \n135:     // AnnotationKeySessionEnd stores the session end timestamp.\n136:     AnnotationKeySessionEnd = \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/session-end\"\n137: \n138:     // AnnotationKeyLastActivity stores the last activity timestamp.\n139:     AnnotationKeyLastActivity = \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/last-activity\"\n140: \n141:     // AnnotationKeyWarmPoolMember indicates if pod is part of warm pool.\n142:     AnnotationKeyWarmPoolMember = \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/warm-pool-member\"\n143: )\n144: ```\n145: \n146: #### Condition Type Constants\n147: \n148: Condition types 用于 status.conditions 数组，遵循 Kubernetes Condition pattern：\n149: \n150: ```go\n151: const (\n152:     // ConditionTypeReady indicates the runtime is ready to accept sessions.\n153:     ConditionTypeReady = \"Ready\"\n154: \n155:     // ConditionTypeAvailable indicates the runtime is available for use.\n156:     ConditionTypeAvailable = \"Available\"\n157: \n158:     // ConditionTypeProgressing indicates the runtime is being created/updated.\n159:     ConditionTypeProgressing = \"Progressing\"\n160: \n161:     // ConditionTypeDegraded indicates the runtime is in a degraded state.\n162:     ConditionTypeDegraded = \"Degraded\"\n163: \n164:     // ConditionTypeSessionActive indicates an active session is running.\n165:     ConditionTypeSessionActive = \"SessionActive\"\n166: )\n167: ```\n168: \n169: #### Condition Reason Constants\n170: \n171: Condition reasons 描述 condition 状态变化的原因：\n172: \n173: ```go\n174: const (\n175:     // ConditionReasonRunning indicates the runtime is running normally.\n176:     ConditionReasonRunning = \"Running\"\n177: \n178:     // ConditionReasonCreating indicates the runtime is being created.\n179:     ConditionReasonCreating = \"Creating\"\n180: \n181:     // ConditionReasonUpdating indicates the runtime is being updated.\n182:     ConditionReasonUpdating = \"Updating\"\n183: \n184:     // ConditionReasonDeleting indicates the runtime is being deleted.\n185:     ConditionReasonDeleting = \"Deleting\"\n186: \n187:     // ConditionReasonError indicates an error occurred.\n188:     ConditionReasonError = \"Error\"\n189: \n190:     // ConditionReasonTimeout indicates a timeout occurred.\n191:     ConditionReasonTimeout = \"Timeout\"\n192: \n193:     // ConditionReasonSessionStarted indicates a session has started.\n194:     ConditionReasonSessionStarted = \"SessionStarted\"\n195: \n196:     // ConditionReasonSessionEnded indicates a session has ended.\n197:     ConditionReasonSessionEnded = \"SessionEnded\"\n198: \n199:     // ConditionReasonIdleTimeout indicates session ended due to idle timeout.\n200:     ConditionReasonIdleTimeout = \"IdleTimeout\"\n201: \n202:     // ConditionReasonMaxDurationReached indicates session ended due to max duration.\n203:     ConditionReasonMaxDurationReached = \"MaxDurationReached\"\n204: )\n205: ```\n206: \n207: #### Default Value Constants\n208: \n209: 默认值常量供 controller 初始化配置使用：\n210: \n211: ```go\n212: const (\n213:     // DefaultSessionTimeout is the default idle session timeout (15 minutes).\n214:     DefaultSessionTimeout = 15 * time.Minute\n215: \n216:     // DefaultMaxSessionDuration is the default maximum session duration (8 hours).\n217:     DefaultMaxSessionDuration = 8 * time.Hour\n218: \n219:     // DefaultWarmPoolSize is the default warm pool size for CodeInterpreter.\n220:     DefaultWarmPoolSize = 0\n221: \n222:     // DefaultAuthMode is the default authentication mode.\n223:     DefaultAuthMode = AuthModePicoD\n224: \n225:     // DefaultProtocol is the default protocol for TargetPort.\n226:     DefaultProtocol = ProtocolTypeHTTP\n227: )\n228: ```\n229: \n230: ## API Contracts\n231: \n232: ### Label Contract\n233: \n234: | Label Key | Value Format | Applied To |\n235: |-----------|--------------|------------|\n236: | `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/owner-runtime` | CR name | Pod, Service |\n237: | `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/owner-kind` | `AgentRuntime` / `CodeInterpreter` | Pod, Service |\n238: | `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/session-id` | UUID | Pod (active session) |\n239: | `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/sandbox-type` | `agent` / `code-interpreter` | Pod |\n240: \n241: ### Annotation Contract\n242: \n243: | Annotation Key | Value Format | Applied To |\n244: |-----------------|--------------|------------|\n245: | `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/auth-mode` | `picod` / `none` | Pod |\n246: | `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/session-start` | RFC3339 timestamp | Pod |\n247: | `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/session-end` | RFC3339 timestamp | Pod |\n248: | `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/last-activity` | RFC3339 timestamp | Pod |\n249: | `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/warm-pool-member` | `true` / `false` | Pod |\n250: \n251: ### Condition Contract\n252: \n253: | Condition Type | Meaning | True Condition |\n254: |-----------------|---------|----------------|\n255: | `Ready` | Runtime ready for sessions | Pod running, no errors |\n256: | `Available` | Runtime available | Ready + healthy |\n257: | `Progressing` | Runtime being modified | Creation/update in progress |\n258: | `Degraded` | Runtime in degraded state | Errors present |\n259: | `SessionActive` | Session running | Pod has active session |\n260: \n261: ## Error Handling\n262: \n263: ### Validation Errors\n264: \n265: | Error Type | Trigger | Response |\n266: |------------|---------|----------|\n267: | Invalid ProtocolType | Value not `HTTP`/`HTTPS` | API server rejects with 400 |\n268: | Invalid AuthModeType | Value not `picod`/`none` | API server rejects with 400 |\n269: | Missing required Port | Port field empty | API server rejects with 400 |\n270: | Invalid port number | Port > 65535 | Controller webhook rejects |\n271: \n272: ### Controller Error Handling\n273: \n274: | Error Type | Handling |\n275: |------------|----------|\n276: | Label/Annotation conflict | Log warning, use CR-specified value |\n277: | Condition update failure | Retry with exponential backoff |\n278: | Default value override | Use CR spec value if specified |\n279: \n280: ## Testing Strategy\n281: \n282: ### Unit Tests\n283: \n284: | Test Category | Coverage |\n285: |---------------|----------|\n286: | Enum constants | Verify all enum values match expected strings |\n287: | DeepCopy | TargetPort.DeepCopy creates independent copy |\n288: | JSON serialization | TargetPort JSON tags correct (camelCase) |\n289: | Default values | Verify default constants match spec defaults |\n290: \n291: ### Test Cases\n292: \n293: ```go\n294: func TestProtocolTypeConstants(t *testing.T) {\n295:     tests := []struct {\n296:         name     string\n297:         constant ProtocolType\n298:         expected string\n299:     }{\n300:         {\"HTTP\", ProtocolTypeHTTP, \"HTTP\"},\n301:         {\"HTTPS\", ProtocolTypeHTTPS, \"HTTPS\"},\n302:     }\n303:     for _, tt := range tests {\n304:         if tt.constant != tt.expected {\n305:             t.Errorf(\"%s: expected %s, got %s\", tt.name, tt.expected, tt.constant)\n306:         }\n307:     }\n308: }\n309: \n310: func TestAuthModeTypeConstants(t *testing.T) {\n311:     tests := []struct {\n312:         name     string\n313:         constant AuthModeType\n314:         expected string\n315:     }{\n316:         {\"PicoD\", AuthModePicoD, \"picod\"},\n317:         {\"None\", AuthModeNone, \"none\"},\n318:     }\n319:     for _, tt := range tests {\n320:         if tt.constant != tt.expected {\n321:             t.Errorf(\"%s: expected %s, got %s\", tt.name, tt.expected, tt.constant)\n322:         }\n323:     }\n324: }\n325: \n326: func TestTargetPortDeepCopy(t *testing.T) {\n327:     original := &TargetPort{\n328:         PathPrefix: \"/api\",\n329:         Name:       \"api\",\n330:         Port:       8080,\n331:         Protocol:   ProtocolTypeHTTP,\n332:     }\n333:     copy := original.DeepCopy()\n334:     \n335:     if copy == original {\n336:         t.Error(\"DeepCopy returned same pointer\")\n337:     }\n338:     if copy.PathPrefix != original.PathPrefix {\n339:         t.Error(\"PathPrefix not copied correctly\")\n340:     }\n341:     \n342:     copy.PathPrefix = \"/modified\"\n343:     if original.PathPrefix == \"/modified\" {\n344:         t.Error(\"DeepCopy is not deep\")\n345:     }\n346: }\n347: \n348: func TestTargetPortJSONSerialization(t *testing.T) {\n349:     tp := TargetPort{\n350:         PathPrefix: \"/api\",\n351:         Name:       \"api\",\n352:         Port:       8080,\n353:         Protocol:   ProtocolTypeHTTP,\n354:     }\n355:     data, err := json.Marshal(tp)\n356:     if err != nil {\n357:         t.Fatalf(\"marshal failed: %v\", err)\n358:     }\n359:     expected := `{\"pathPrefix\":\"/api\",\"name\":\"api\",\"port\":8080,\"protocol\":\"HTTP\"}`\n360:     if string(data) != expected {\n361:         t.Errorf(\"expected %s, got %s\", expected, string(data))\n362:     }\n363: }\n364: \n365: func TestLabelConstants(t *testing.T) {\n366:     if LabelKeyOwnerRuntime != \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/owner-runtime\" {\n367:         t.Error(\"LabelKeyOwnerRuntime mismatch\")\n368:     }\n369:     if LabelKeySessionID != \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/session-id\" {\n370:         t.Error(\"LabelKeySessionID mismatch\")\n371:     }\n372: }\n373: \n374: func TestConditionTypeConstants(t *testing.T) {\n375:     if ConditionTypeReady != \"Ready\" {\n376:         t.Error(\"ConditionTypeReady mismatch\")\n377:     }\n378:     if ConditionTypeAvailable != \"Available\" {\n379:         t.Error(\"ConditionTypeAvailable mismatch\")\n380:     }\n381: }\n382: \n383: func TestDefaultConstants(t *testing.T) {\n384:     if DefaultSessionTimeout != 15*time.Minute {\n385:         t.Error(\"DefaultSessionTimeout mismatch\")\n386:     }\n387:     if DefaultMaxSessionDuration != 8*time.Hour {\n388:         t.Error(\"DefaultMaxSessionDuration mismatch\")\n389:     }\n390:     if DefaultAuthMode != AuthModePicoD {\n391:         t.Error(\"DefaultAuthMode mismatch\")\n392:     }\n393:     if DefaultProtocol != ProtocolTypeHTTP {\n394:         t.Error(\"DefaultProtocol mismatch\")\n395:     }\n396: }\n397: ```\n398: \n399: ### Integration Tests\n400: \n401: - Verify labels/annotations applied to pods match constant definitions\n402: - Verify conditions in CRD status use defined type constants\n403: - Verify CRD YAML generation includes enum validation\n404: \n405: ## File Structure\n406: \n407: ```\n408: pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/\n409:   shared_types.go      — 共享类型、枚举、常量定义\n410:   zz_generated.deepcopy.go — DeepCopy 方法（由 controller-gen 生成）\n411:   types_test.go        — 单元测试\n412: ```\n413: \n414: ### shared_types.go Structure\n415: \n416: ```go\n417: package v1alpha1\n418: \n419: import \"time\"\n420: \n421: // ============================================================================\n422: // Type Definitions\n423: // ============================================================================\n424: \n425: type ProtocolType string\n426: const (\n427:     ProtocolTypeHTTP  ProtocolType = \"HTTP\"\n428:     ProtocolTypeHTTPS ProtocolType = \"HTTPS\"\n429: )\n430: \n431: type AuthModeType string\n432: const (\n433:     AuthModePicoD AuthModeType = \"picod\"\n434:     AuthModeNone  AuthModeType = \"none\"\n435: )\n436: \n437: type TargetPort struct {\n438:     PathPrefix string      `json:\"pathPrefix,omitempty\"`\n439:     Name       string      `json:\"name,omitempty\"`\n440:     Port       uint32      `json:\"port\"`\n441:     Protocol   ProtocolType `json:\"protocol\"`\n442: }\n443: \n444: // ============================================================================\n445: // Label Constants\n446: // ============================================================================\n447: \n448: const (\n449:     LabelKeyOwnerRuntime     = \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/owner-runtime\"\n450:     LabelKeyOwnerKind        = \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/owner-kind\"\n451:     LabelKeySessionID        = \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/session-id\"\n452:     LabelKeySandboxType      = \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/sandbox-type\"\n453:     LabelKeySandboxTypeAgent = \"agent\"\n454:     LabelKeySandboxTypeCodeInterpreter = \"code-interpreter\"\n455: )\n456: \n457: // ============================================================================\n458: // Annotation Constants\n459: // ============================================================================\n460: \n461: const (\n462:     AnnotationKeyAuthMode       = \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/auth-mode\"\n463:     AnnotationKeySessionStart   = \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/session-start\"\n464:     AnnotationKeySessionEnd     = \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/session-end\"\n465:     AnnotationKeyLastActivity   = \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/last-activity\"\n466:     AnnotationKeyWarmPoolMember = \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/warm-pool-member\"\n467: )\n468: \n469: // ============================================================================\n470: // Condition Constants\n471: // ============================================================================\n472: \n473: const (\n474:     ConditionTypeReady        = \"Ready\"\n475:     ConditionTypeAvailable    = \"Available\"\n476:     ConditionTypeProgressing  = \"Progressing\"\n477:     ConditionTypeDegraded     = \"Degraded\"\n478:     ConditionTypeSessionActive = \"SessionActive\"\n479: )\n480: \n481: const (\n482:     ConditionReasonRunning            = \"Running\"\n483:     ConditionReasonCreating           = \"Creating\"\n484:     ConditionReasonUpdating           = \"Updating\"\n485:     ConditionReasonDeleting           = \"Deleting\"\n486:     ConditionReasonError              = \"Error\"\n487:     ConditionReasonTimeout            = \"Timeout\"\n488:     ConditionReasonSessionStarted     = \"SessionStarted\"\n489:     ConditionReasonSessionEnded       = \"SessionEnded\"\n490:     ConditionReasonIdleTimeout        = \"IdleTimeout\"\n491:     ConditionReasonMaxDurationReached = \"MaxDurationReached\"\n492: )\n493: \n494: // ============================================================================\n495: // Default Value Constants\n496: // ============================================================================\n497: \n498: const (\n499:     DefaultSessionTimeout     = 15 * time.Minute\n500:     DefaultMaxSessionDuration = 8 * time.Hour\n501:     DefaultWarmPoolSize       = 0\n502: )\n503: \n504: var (\n505:     DefaultAuthMode  = AuthModePicoD\n506:     DefaultProtocol  = ProtocolTypeHTTP\n507: )\n508: ```\n509: \n510: ## Generation Commands\n511: \n512: | Command | Output |\n513: |---------|--------|\n514: | `make generate` | DeepCopy code in `zz_generated.deepcopy.go` |\n515: | `go build ./pkg/apis/...` | Compile verification |\n516: | `go test ./pkg/apis/...` | Unit test execution |\n517: \n518: ## References\n519: \n520: - Source: `/tmp/agentcube-ref/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/`\n521: - Kubernetes API Conventions: https://git.k8s.io/community/contributors/devel/sig-architecture/api-conventions.md\n522: - Kubebuilder Book: https://book.kubebuilder.io/